<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Контакты - Вакация</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bellota:wght@400;700&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css?v=<%= Date.now() %>">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc; color: var(--text-dark); }
        .ballone { font-family: 'Bellota', cursive; position: relative; display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4; }
        .ballone svg { position: absolute; bottom: -8px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 12px; }

        .contacts-hero {
            padding: 120px 0 100px;
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 0 0 60px 60px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }
        .contacts-hero h1 { font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-dark); margin: 0; letter-spacing: -2px; }
        .contacts-hero p { color: #64748b; font-size: 18px; max-width: 700px; margin: 24px auto 0; line-height: 1.6; }

        .contacts-container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 40px auto 120px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .contacts-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .contact-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 32px 20px;
            border-radius: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .contact-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.1); border-color: var(--light-purple); }
        .contact-icon {
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            background: var(--light-purple);
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .contact-card p { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-dark); margin: 0; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; width: 100%; }
        .contact-card a { color: var(--text-dark); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease; display: block; width: 100%; }
        .contact-card a:hover { color: var(--primary-purple); }

        /* Карта */
        .map-container {
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            border-radius: 32px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .map-container iframe {
            width: 100%;
            height: 450px;
            border: 0;
            display: block;
        }
        .map-address {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        .map-address strong {
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        .social-cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 80px;
            padding: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #f3f0ff 100%);
            border-radius: 48px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-purple);
        }
        .social-cta h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--primary-purple); letter-spacing: -1.5px; font-family: 'Bellota', cursive; }
        .social-cta p { color: #4b5563; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 30px; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; line-height: 1.6; }
        .social-buttons { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 24px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
        .social-btn {
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 16px;
            background: #0077FF;
            color: white;
        }
        .social-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        
        /* Увеличенная иконка VK */
        .social-btn svg {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
        }

        .bg-decor-icon { position: absolute; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1; opacity: 0.3; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .contacts-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; }
            .contacts-hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .social-cta { padding: 40px 20px; }
            .social-cta h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main>
        <section class="contacts-hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Мы всегда на <span class="ballone">связи<svg viewBox="0 0 100 12" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,10 Q50,0 100,10" stroke="var(--primary-purple)" stroke-width="6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span></h1>
                <p>Остались вопросы? Хотите предложить сотрудничество? Нужна помощь? Напишите нам — мы ответим быстро.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="contacts-container">
            <div class="contacts-grid">
                <div class="contact-card">
                    <div class="contact-icon">
                        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-purple)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
                            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <p><a href="mailto:protrafficgroup@yandex.ru">protrafficgroup@yandex.ru</a></p>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-card">
                    <div class="contact-icon">
                        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary-purple)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <p><a href="tel:+79123403917">+7 (912) 340-39-17</a></p>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-card">
                    <div class="contact-icon">
                        <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--primary-purple)">
                            <path d="M13.162 18.994c-6.098 0-9.57-4.172-9.714-11.109h3.01c.107 5.089 2.346 7.24 4.121 7.795V7.885h2.835v4.454c1.734-.185 3.563-2.164 4.177-4.454h2.835a8.18 8.18 0 0 1-3.83 5.787 8.575 8.575 0 0 1 4.422 6.322h-3.11c-.463-1.443-1.613-2.556-3.03-2.704v2.704h-1.816z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <p><a href="https://vk.com/pro.traffic.group" target="_blank">pro.traffic.group</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Карта с адресом Pro Traffic Group -->
            <div class="map-container">
                <iframe 
                    src="https://yandex.ru/map-widget/v1/?text=Россия, г. Оренбург, улица Терешковой, 281/1к2&z=17" 
                    allowfullscreen="true" 
                    loading="lazy">
                </iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="map-address">
                <strong>Pro Traffic Group</strong> — Россия, г. Оренбург, улица Терешковой, 281/1к2
            </div>

            <section class="social-cta">
                <div class="bg-decor-icon" style="top: 15%; left: 10%;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--primary-purple)"><path d="M12 0L14.59 9.41L24 12L14.59 14.59L12 24L9.41 14.59L0 12L9.41 9.41L12 0Z"/></svg></div>
                <div class="bg-decor-icon" style="bottom: 20%; right: 10%;"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--primary-purple)"><path d="M12 0L14.59 9.41L24 12L14.59 14.59L12 24L9.41 14.59L0 12L9.41 9.41L12 0Z"/></svg></div>
                
                <h2>Будьте в центре событий!</h2>
                <p>Подписывайтесь на наши соцсети, чтобы не пропустить самые крутые мероприятия и эксклюзивные предложения.</p>
                <div class="social-buttons">
                    <a href="https://vk.com/pro.traffic.group" target="_blank" class="social-btn vk">
                        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                            <path d="M13.162 18.994c-6.098 0-9.57-4.172-9.714-11.109h3.01c.107 5.089 2.346 7.24 4.121 7.795V7.885h2.835v4.454c1.734-.185 3.563-2.164 4.177-4.454h2.835a8.18 8.18 0 0 1-3.83 5.787 8.575 8.575 0 0 1 4.422 6.322h-3.11c-.463-1.443-1.613-2.556-3.03-2.704v2.704h-1.816z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>